{"title":"Old Man Mountain Painted Hills Anodizing on Basket and Axle Pack","link":"https://theradavist.com/old-man-mountain-painted-hills-anodizing-on-basket-and-axle-pack/","date":1724338729000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/Old_Man_Mountain_Anodizing.jpg?fit=1200,1440&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/Old_Man_Mountain_Anodizing.jpg?w=1920&amp;quality=75 1920w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/Old_Man_Mountain_Anodizing.jpg?resize=1200,900&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/Old_Man_Mountain_Anodizing.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/Old_Man_Mountain_Anodizing.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>For MADE 2024 Old Man Mountain turned to its local landscape for inspiration. Central Oregon is home to the Painted Hills, a stunning geologic feature made of mineral rich soils compacted into layers upon layers of striated color. OMM took these colors and made a special series of <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=9810ede6-4922-46d9-b096-e2993c490cc6&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Foldmanmountain.com%2Fproduct%2Fpainted-hills-anodize%2F\" target=\"_blank\">Axle Pack</a> and <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=9810ede6-4922-46d9-b096-e2993c490cc6&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Foldmanmountain.com%2Fproduct%2Fpainted-hills-anodize%2F\" target=\"_blank\">Baskets</a>, along with Astral Outback wheelsets.</p>\n<p>The parts are super limited to just 12 sets of Axle Pack, 12 Baskets. There are a few Baskets and Axle Packs available <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=9810ede6-4922-46d9-b096-e2993c490cc6&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Foldmanmountain.com%2Fproduct%2Fpainted-hills-anodize%2F\" target=\"_blank\">online</a>, the rest are available in person at MADE 2024. Prices are the same as normal.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/MADE_Custom-Ano_Astral-3.jpg?fit=1200,1440&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/MADE_Custom-Ano_Astral-3.jpg?w=1920&amp;quality=75 1920w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/MADE_Custom-Ano_Astral-3.jpg?resize=1200,900&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/MADE_Custom-Ano_Astral-3.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/MADE_Custom-Ano_Astral-3.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Also matching this kit are Astralâ€™s <a href=\"https://astralcycling.com/collections/the-outback-family/products/outback-wheelset-white-industries-cld-hubs\" target=\"_blank\">Outback wheelsets</a>, which are only available in person at MADE 2024.</p>\n<p>Check it all out at <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=9810ede6-4922-46d9-b096-e2993c490cc6&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Foldmanmountain.com%2Fproduct%2Fpainted-hills-anodize%2F\" target=\"_blank\">Old Man Mountain</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/old-man-mountain-painted-hills-anodizing-on-basket-and-axle-pack/\">Old Man Mountain Painted Hills Anodizing on Basket and Axle Pack</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"4ed200d0294247e0da42c2d47d3a9579529941775374402a8a69cd585ee76f04","category":"Cycling"}